  ('judicial-a9db9bda-moex-00155', 'judicial-a9db9bda', 'judicial-a9db9bda-moex-111-4f961f01', 'sub-judicial-a9db9bda-06', NULL, 'essay', '許多收容人因早期生命經驗的影響而誤入歧途，請詳述 Tyber與 Holmes
